name: Purpose International Tactical Hedged Equity Fund
longDescription: The fund seeks to provide shareholders with (i) consistent long-term capital appreciation with an attractive risk-adjusted rate of return investing in a portfolio of international listed equities; and (ii) provide less volatility and low correlation to international equity markets by hedging the funds exposure to overall market risk. The fund invests in a portfolio of international listed equities, and provide less volatility and low correlation to international equity markets by hedging the fund exposure to overall market risk.
